# data-models

## Core Data Structures

### Game State Models
- Centralized in `src/store/gameStore.ts`
- Match scoring system tracking progress to 100 points
- Round-based gameplay progression states
- Fixed-limit betting rule structures
- Game history with win/loss record tracking

### Hand Evaluation Models
- Located in `src/lib/poker/handEvaluator.ts`
- Card combination detection structures
- Hand strength calculation models
- Specialized ranking value system for tie-breaking
- Comparative hand scoring system

### Gameplay Flow Models
- Defined in `src/lib/poker/gameLogic.ts`
- Betting round state management
- Turn-based progression structure
- Pot and chip distribution models
- Hand progression states:
  - Deal
  - Initial betting
  - Draw
  - Final betting
  - Showdown

### AI Decision Models
- Implemented in `src/lib/poker/aiOpponent.ts`
- Hand strength evaluation structures
- Risk assessment models based on pot odds
- Strategic decision trees for betting/folding
- Bluffing probability models
- Dynamic bet sizing calculations

